<hr>
Every student has had to ask a question before. In school our teachers always told us that there was no such thing as a dumb question. But that is a blatant lie. There are definitely dumb questions. As we students transition into industry, we must break the habit of asking dumb questions since there is no teacher required to give us the answer. 


